data.description: Motivated seller-will consider all offers! Buy now before rates go down and home prices go up! Enjoy stunning views from the 4 bedroom, 4 bath home with a large shop on 2.74+/- acres!  This 2664+/- sq. ft. home offers a lovely front yard leading to the entry and an open floor plan including a large living room with bay window and built-in entertainment center, dining area with matching bay window and an informal breakfast area that takes you to the large kitchen with tile counter tops and back splash, breakfast bar and a convenient laundry room and separate walk-in pantry.  Down the hall you'll find 1 guest bedroom and a guest bathroom and both master bedrooms and master bathrooms.  The 2nd master bedroom is handicapped accessible with french doors, built-in shelves and a walk-in closet all of which were custom built by the VA and there is a custom huge master bath that is fully handicapped accessible with tiled shower and stained glass window.  There is 1 guest bedroom and bath on the opposite end of the home that is great for in-laws or overnight company.  From the back patio you can sit under the pergola and enjoy a good book or use the side patio to entertain. The views are wonderful from either patio!  Enjoy fresh fruit from the trees by the huge shop!  Yummy Apricots, Peaches, Nectarines, Plums and Oranges!  The shop is perfect for gardening tools, workshop or to use for storage.  Come and take a stroll to appreciate everything this home has to offer!
